title: Good Directions 9602P Bass With Lure Weathervane - Polished Copper
description: It's every fisherman's dream: a beautiful bass taking a bite of a lure! Now you can enjoy catching sight of this big-bodied fish on the rooftop of your house, barn, garage, or cupola. Our Good Directions' artisans use Old World techniques to handcraft this fully functional, standard-size weathervane that's unsurpassed in style, quality and durability. A great gift for fishing enthusiasts!
